Create Cultural Object

To create new cultural object:

  1. Select Create / Upload button
  2. Select the context you want the cultural object to be created
  3. Select the type of the cultural object you want to created
  4. Fill the mandatory data
  5. Press the Create button.

The cultural object page will be opened where you can fill the cultural object data and save.
